{"tid":637373,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"超血腥恐怖遊戲《痛苦地獄Agony》將於5/29於PS4平台上推出！","createTime":"2018-04-21T17:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T06:08:19.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"36a0eb57b74655eec92b10d1c154016b560500d3","tid":637373,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:42:14.000Z","msg":"據了解，PS4 之遊戲版本會稍作修飾，刪減部份血腥和裸露元素，而PC版本則會透過PATCH解放所有元素，驚嚇度爆棚。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201804/b6df4ea57b40f4a4cca2ec34e9d3b99b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201804%2Fb6df4ea57b40f4a4cca2ec34e9d3b99b.JPG&h=3feac1fe&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nSource：<br />\n<a href=\"https://wccftech.com/horror-game-agony-launch-may29/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwccftech.com%2Fhorror-game-agony-launch-may29%2F&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e03036f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://wccftech.com/horror-game-agony-launch-may29/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcgamer.com/amp/pc-version-of-agony-will-have-optional-patch-to-remove-censorship/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcgamer.com%2Famp%2Fpc-version-of-agony-will-have-optional-patch-to-remove-censorship%2F&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=30e751de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcgamer.com/amp/pc-version-of-agony-will-have-optional-patch-to-remove-censorship/</a>"},{"pid":"3a53a0d6d9941fcda6002480d982737d8bfe3d5d","tid":637373,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:46:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>連結內容含有血腥、怪奇、暴力元素請慎入</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=38097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D60596%26snA%3D38097&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8a99a121\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=60596&amp;snA=38097</a><br />\n<br />\n之前有宣佈過延期的《苦痛地獄Agony》<br />\n今日正式宣佈將於5/29在PS4/XBO/PC上發售<br />\n要特別注意得是版本的差別<br />\n在家用主機的版本是經過修飾過得較不血腥的版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPC版本開發者會另外放個無修正版本的Patch給玩家選擇使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會增加這個限制主要是開發商想在分級上通過原先設定的目標（應該是M級）<br />\n然而當初的版本有刑求、裸露、血腥等畫面<br />\n因此毫無疑問會是列在AO等級<br />\n我想這也是當初3/30發售跳票的原因之一<br />\n<br />\n發售日公開預告<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yKTOfRypuhQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyKTOfRypuhQ&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f51cd543\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yKTOfRypuhQ</a><br />\n<br />\n官方實機遊玩影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aSGIaiuqb-Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaSGIaiuqb-Y&d=hxg47QoceM5mP1F6l8fP6rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=7a79a58b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aSGIaiuqb-Y</a>"},{"pid":"4c052c114821c78545404c9a7cf92a320a621e8b","tid":637373,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:50:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網民回應</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n稀哩嘩啦なUiKen ：<br />\n<br />\n這邊做個解釋為什麼PC版會跟家機版比較不一樣好了(也牽扯到延期的原因)<br />\n<br />\n根據官方自己的進度報告，原先的版本分級是屬於AO(Audlt Only)，也就是成人限定，在這個分級的遊戲＂只能＂出在PC上，為了達成3平台都能上架，所以官方不得不把遊戲內容做刪減來降低分級標準，為了把遊戲內容刪減到家機平台也能上架的標準，在刪減的選擇需要花上不少時間，所以原先的日期跳票<br />\n(以上都是官方的進度報告裡的)<br />\n<br />\n另外...Patch、Patch、Patch，感覺很重要所以說個3次好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nハレンチ・von・ヤロウ：<br />\n<br />\n「AO只能出PC上」是商業因素，不是硬性規定<br />\nSONY,MS,任天堂,Valve為了維護品牌形象，會拒絕販賣AO遊戲<br />\n如果你能避開這些公司的平台，獨立販售也不會有法律上的問題<br />\n只不過銷售管道有限就較難賺錢<br />\n但是也有例外<br />\n像是GTA:SA就曾經因為Hot Coffee事件而被列為AO遊戲<br />\n當時SONY沒有阻止遊戲繼續販賣<br />\nRockstar給零售店兩個選擇<br />\n一個是補上AO貼紙繼續賣，不然可以退貨<br />\n遊戲夠熱門就還是會有店家敢進貨販賣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPeace：<br />\n<br />\n我在他們的kickstarter看到他們說<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">贊助者會有獨家更新</span></strong></span> 不論是PC PS4 XBOX 都可以玩到『完整版』<br />\nPC我可以理解補丁更新 那PS4平台要用什麼方式讓只有特定PSN ID取得更新或DLC？？"},{"pid":"63c2a6b82ff126b97b7c4460dacb005e176f6e75","tid":637373,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T18:37:51.000Z","msg":"21:9 1440p curved mon with 1080ti AMD 1800x is ready <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff8750d46fdcbceaadab5c15964725dedc794a4","tid":637373,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865519810b966bdec6ea0a69f9b5a8f10da916a2","tid":637373,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"玩pc版是常識吧"}]}